saipeAPI
  • Reference

Possible variables for us, state, and county-level datasets

A data frame contains possible variables and variable labels.

saipe_vars

Format

An object of class tbl_df (inherits from tbl, data.frame) with 47 rows and 5 columns.

Source

http://api.census.gov/data/timeseries/poverty/saipe/variables.html

Examples

# To get a vector of possible variables:
saipeAPI::saipe_vars$Name
